flow "I want to build a web application to show how different activities impact continuous delivery.  The goal is to show the dependencies that exist between activities. These dependencies could be tooling, behaviors, or culture. The opening screen should show a box that says 'start your CD journey.' From there's it should expand to show the dependencies of CD using the information from MinimumCD.org Then, when the use clicks on one of the dependencies, it will expand to show what it depends on. Each of the practices defined will also have their own dependencies, so we need a data structure that treats all practices as potential parents and children with CD as the top level parent.  Provide a plan "
